Titmuss (London: Allen and Unwin, 1987).亦参见William E. Upton, "Altruism, Attribution, and Intrinsic Motivation in the Recruitment of Blood Donors," Ph.D. diss., Cornell University, 1973.

　　第四○页，七百万美国小孩一夕之间消失：参见Jeffrey Liebman, "Who Are the Ineligible EITC Recipients?" National Tax Journal 53 (2000), pp. 1165-86. Liebman's paper was citing John Szilagyi, "Where Some of Those Dependents Went," 1990 Research Conference Report: How Do We Affect Taxpayer Behavior? (Internal Revenue Service: March 1991), pp.162-63.

　　第四一—五一页，芝加哥教师作弊事件：这项研究对关键测验的背景有详细的说明，研究内容可参考以下两篇论文：Brian A. Jacob and Steven D. Levitt, "Rotten Apples: An Investigation of the Prevalence and Predictors of Teacher Cheating," Quarterly Journal of Economics 118, no. 3 (2003), pp. 843-77; and Brian A. Jacob and Steven D. Levitt, "Catching Cheating Teachers: The Results of an Unusual Experiment in Implementing Theory," Brookings-Wharton Papers on Urban Affairs, 2003, pp. 185-209.／第四二页，欧克兰五年级学童的放水老师：取材于作者对欧克兰公立学校一位前助理督学的访谈。／第四六页，北卡罗莱纳州老师的作弊情况：参见G. H. Gay, "Standardized Tests: Irregularities in Administering of Tests Affect Test Results," Journal of Instructional Psychology 17, no. 2 (1990), pp. 93-103.／第五○—五一页， 芝加哥学校执行长邓肯的故事大致根据作者的访谈，亦参见Amy D'Orio, "The Outsider Comes In," District Administration: The Magazine for K-12 Education Leaders, August 2002; and various Chicago Tribune articles by Ray Quintanilla.

　　第五二—五三页，乔治亚大学的篮球测验事件之所以曝光，是由于该校针对全国大学运动委员会的调查而公布的长达一千五百页的文件。

　　第五三—五九页，相扑的作弊：参见Mark Duggan and Steven D. Levitt, "Winning Isn't Everything: Corruption in Sumo Wrestling," American Economic Review 92, no. 5 (December 2002), pp. 1594-1605.／第五三—五九页，有关相扑的知识可参考：Mina Hall, The Big Book of Sumo (Berkeley, Calif.: Stonebridge Press, 1997); Keisuke Itai, Nakabon (Tokyo: Shogakkan Press, 2000); and Onaruto, Yaocho (Tokyo: Line Books, 2000).／第五八页，两位揭发相扑弊案的选手离奇死亡：参见Sheryl WuDunn, "Sumo Wrestlers (They're BIG) Facing a Hard Fall," New York Times, June 28, 1996; and Anthony Spaeth, "Sumo Quake: Japan's Revered Sport Is Marred by Charges of Tax Evasion, March Fixing, Ties to Organized Crime, and Two Mysterious Deaths," reporting by Irene M. Kunii and Hiroki Tashiro, Time (International Edition), September 30, 1996.

　　第五九—六四页，贝果人费尔曼：费尔曼希望找一位对他的资料有兴趣的经济学者，结果引起李维特的注意。（好几位其他学者并未回应。）本书两位作者随后亲自到华盛顿参观费尔曼的业务。他们在这方面的研究整理为以下一篇文章，内容与本章所述大致相同：Stephen J. Dubner and Steven D. Levitt, "What the Bagel Man Saw," The New York Times Magazine, June 6, 2004. 李维特也撰写了一篇相关的学术论文 "An Economist Sells Bagel: A Case Study in Profit Maximization, National Bureau of Economic Research working paper 2006."。／第六一页，「海滩啤酒」研究，参见Richard H. Thaler, "Mental Accounting and Consumer Choice," Marketing Science 4 (Summer 1985), pp. 119-2l4；也值得一读的是Richard H. Thaler, The Winner's Curse: Paradoxes and Anomalies of Economic Life (New York: Free Press, 1992).

２三Ｋ党与房地产仲介有何相似处？

　　第六五—七四页，泄露三Ｋ党的秘密：自从《苹果橘子经济学》第一版发行之后，这一节做了重大的修正，因为作者发现甘乃迪——在他的回忆录《撕下面具的三Ｋ党》，以及在和作者的访谈中——做错误的表示，说他自己担任渗透和打击三Ｋ党的角色。（有关这件事的完整说明，详第二四五页〔「欺世盗名」一文，NYT Jan. 8, 2006〕。）有关整个三Ｋ党历史，详Col. Winfield Jones, Knights of the Ku Klux Klan, 1865-1965 (Garden City, NY: Doubleday, 1965); Wyn Craig Wade, The Fiery Cross: The Ku Klux Klan in America (New York: Simon & Schuster, 1987)；及许多文献。和甘乃迪关系最密切的作品包括Southern Exposure (Garden City, NY: Doubleday, 1946; republished in 1911 by Florida Atlantic university Press, 1990)和The Klan Unmasked (Boca Raton: Florida Atlantic University Press, 1990)，原先出版时是I Rode with the Ku Klux Klan (London: Arco Publishers, 1954)。Ben Green, Before His Time: The Untold Story of Harry T. Moore, America's First Civil Rights Martyr (New York: Simon & Schuster, 1999) 也很有用。甘乃迪有关三Ｋ党、「布朗」报告，和其他相关文件的档案，可以在好几个档案室里找到，包括Schomburg Center for Research in Black Culture, a public library in New York City; the George State University Library in Atlanta; and the archives of the Anti-Defamation League in New York City. 皮尔森的"Washington Merry-Go-Round"广播节目稿可以在http://www.aladin.wrlc.org/gsdl/collect/pearson/pearson.shtml找到。

　　第七五—七六页，定期寿险费率参见Jeffrey R. Brown and Austan Goolsbee, "Does the Internet Make Markets More Competitive? Evidence from the Life Insurance Industry," Journal of Political Economy 110, no. 3 (June 2002), pp. 481-507.

　　第七六页，诚如美国最高法院法官布兰迪斯所言：「阳光是最好的杀菌剂。」参见Louis D. Brandeis, Other People's Money—and How Bankers Use It (New York: Frederick A. Stokes, 1914).

　　第七六页，全新二手车：这一理论以及今日我们对资讯不对称性的认识，来自阿克洛夫（George A. Akerlof）于一九六六至一九六七年在柏克莱担任助理教授的头一年所写的一篇论文："The Market for 'Lemons': Quality Uncertainty and the Market Mechanism," Quarterly Journal of Economics, August 1970. 这篇论文曾被退稿三次——据阿克洛夫事后回忆，其中两家期刊告诉他，它们「不刊登以这类芝麻小事为主题的论文」。大约三十年后，阿克洛夫因这篇论文而获得诺贝尔经济学奖。

　　第七八页，安隆录音带：目前这些录音带可以在下述网站听到http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2004/06/01/eveningnews/main620626.shtml. 亦参见Richard A. Oppel Jr., "Enron Traders on Grandma Millie and Making Out Like Bandits," New York Times, June 13, 2004.

　　第七九页，血管扩张术有必要吗？参见Gina Kolata, "New Heart Studies Question the Value of Opening Arteries," New York Times, March 21, 2004.

　　第七九—八五页，房地产仲介问题：参见Steven D. Levitt and Chad Syverson, "Market Distortions When Agents Are Better Informed: A Theoretical and Empirical Exploration of the Value of Information in Real-Estate Transactions," National Bureau of Economic Research working paper, 2005.

　　第八五页，洛特，半公开的种族隔离主义者？有关洛特发表此项言论的场景，参见Dan Goodgame and Karen Tumulty, "Lott: Tripped Up by History," Time.com/cnn.com, December 16, 2002.

　　第八六—八八页，〈智者生存〉：参见Steven D, Levitt, "Testing Theories of Discrimination: Evidence from The Weakest Link," Journal of Law and Economics 17 (October 2004), pp. 431-52.／第八七页，偏好性歧视理论首见于Gary S. Becker, The Economics of Discrimination (Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 1957).／第七九页，资讯性歧视源自一些论文，包括Edmund Phelps, "A Statistical Theory of Racism and Sexism," American Economic Review 62, no. 4 (1972), pp. 659-61; and Kenneth Arrow, "The Theory of Discrimination," Discrimination in Labor Markets, ed. Orley Ashenfelter and Albert Rees (Princeton, N.J.: Princeton University Press, 1973).

　　第八八—九一页，线上约会：参见Gu©anter J. Hitsch, Ali Horta©jsu, and Dan Ariely, "What Makes You Click: An Empirical Analysis of Online Dating," University of Chicago working paper, 2005.

　　第九二页，选民在丁金斯对朱利安尼的选举民调中说谎：参见Timur Kuran, Private Truths Public Lies: The Social Consequences of Preference Falsification (Cambridge, Mass.: Harvard University Press, 1995); also Kevin Sack, "Governor Joins Dinkins Attack Against Rival," New York Times, October 27, 1989; and Sam Roberts, "Uncertainty over Polls Clouds Strategy in Mayor Race," New York Times, October 31, 1989.

　　第九二页，选民在杜克的选举民调中说谎：参见Kuran, Private Truths, Public Lies, also Peter Applebome, "Republican Quits Louisiana Race in Effort to Defeat Ex-Klansman," New York Times, October 5, 1990; and Peter Applebome, "Racial Politics in South's Contests: Hot Wind of Hate or Last Gasp?" New York Times, November 5, 1990.

　　第九二页，杜克，滥用资讯的高手：相关的资料如Karen Henderson, "David Duke's Work-Release Program," National Public Radio, May 14, 2004; John McQuaid, "Duke's Decline," New Orleans Times-Picayune, April 13, 2003.

３为何毒贩还和母亲住一起？

　　第九三页，盖博瑞斯的传统观点：参见 "The Concept of the Conventional Wisdom," the second chapter of The Affluent Society (Boston: Houghton Mifflin, 1958).

　　第九四页，史奈德与数百万无家可归的游民：史奈德的社会运动所引发的争议广受报导，尤其是科罗拉多的报纸在一九八○年代初期以及一九九○史奈德自杀那年。有关此一课题的概览可参见Gary S. Becker and Guity Nashat Becker, "How the Homeless 'Crisis' Was Hyped," in The Economics of Life (New York: McGraw-Hill, 1997), pp. 175-76；本章资料摘自相同作者一九九四年发表于Business Week的文章。

　　第九五页，口臭问题受到重视：李施德霖有趣的发展史在以下的著作中有精采的叙述：Twenty Ads That Shook the World: The Century's Most Groundbreaking Advertising and How It Changed Us All (New York: Crown, 2000), pp. 60-69.

　　第九五页，小布希刻意表现像个牛仔：参见Paul Krugman, "New Year's Resolutions," New York Times, December 26, 2003.

　　第九五页，强暴案并不如一般所想像那样多：二○○二全国犯罪调查在设计上特别注意受访者的诚实回答，结果发现妇女一生中成为强暴或非自愿性行为受害者的机率是八分之一（而不是论者所宣称的三分之一），至于男性的风险则是四十分之一，而不是论者所宣称的九分之一。

　　第九六页，犯罪并没那么多：参见Mark Niesse, "Report Says Atlanta Underreported Crimes to Help Land 1996 Olympics," Associated Press, February 20, 2004.

　　第九七—一一二页，凡卡德希深入贩毒帮派：凡卡德希目前为哥伦比亚大学社会学与非裔美国人研究的教授。／第九七—一○二页，凡卡德希的亲身经历大都根据作者的访谈；亦参见Jordan Marsh, "The Gang Way," Chicago Reader, August 8, 1997; and Robert L. Kaiser, "The Science of Fitting In," Chicago Tribune, December 10, 2000.／第一○三—一一二页，快克帮派的细节参见以下四篇论文：Sudhir Alladi Venkatesh and Steven D. Levitt: "The Financial Activities of an Urban Street Gang," Quarterly Journal of Economics 115, no. 3 (August 2000), pp. 755-89; "'Are We a Family or a Business?' History and Disjuncture in the Urban American Street Gang," Theory and Society 29 (Autumn 2000), pp. 427-62; "Growing Up in the Projects: The Economic Lives of a Cohort of Men Who Came of Age in Chicago Public Housing," American Economic Review 91, no. 2 (2001), pp. 79-84; and "The Political Economy of an American Street Gang," American Bar Foundation working paper, 1998. See also Sudhir Alladi Venkatesh, American Project: The Rise and Fall of a Modern Ghetto (Cambridge, Mass.: Harvard University Press 2000)／第一○七页，毒品交易是美国最危险的工作：根据劳工统计局的资料，美国最危险的十个合法行业是伐木工、渔夫、飞机与船舶驾驶、结构金属工、司机／业务人员、屋顶修理工、电力装设人员、农场工人、建筑工人、卡车司机。

　　第一一二页，尼龙丝袜的发明：杜邦的一位年经化学家卡若瑟斯（Wallace Carothers）经过七年的研究后，发明一种方法将液态聚合体由微小喷嘴吹出，产生超强的纤维，这就是尼龙。几年后，杜邦开始在纽约与伦敦推出尼龙丝袜。不过和通俗说法不同的是，这种奇迹性纤维的名称NYLON并非取自纽约与伦敦这两大城市名字的组合，也不是谣传中调侃当年称霸丝绸市场的日本：「日本佬，这回你们输了」（Now You've Lost, Old Nippon）的缩写。这个名字其实只不过是「别跑」（No Run）的谐音，暗示这种新袜子其实不耐穿，不过这个缺陷几乎丝毫未使它的成功有所逊色。可惜长期为忧郁症所苦的卡若瑟斯未能目睹自己的心血开花结果：他于一九三七年服氰化物自杀。参见Matthew E. Hermes, Enough for One Life-time: Wallace Carothers, Inventor of Nylon (Philadelphia: Chemical Heritage Foundation, 1996).

　　第一一三页，快克暱称：大达拉斯酒类与药物滥用委员会（The Greater Dallas Council on Alcohol and Drug Abuse）曾就古柯碱的街头俗名整理出相当有趣的索引。古柯碱粉的别名有：Badrock, Bazooka, Beam, Berni, Bernice, Big C, Blast, Blizzard, Blow, Blunt, Bouncing Powder, Bump, C, Caballo, Caine, Candy, Caviar, Charlie, Chicken Scratch, Coca, Cocktail, Coconut, Coke, Cola, Damablanca, Dust, Flake, Flex, Florida Snow, Foo Foo, Freeze, G-Rock, Girl, Goofball, Happy Dust, Happy Powder, Happy Trails, Heaven, King, Lady, Lady Caine, Late Night, Line, Mama Coca, Marching Dust/Powder, Mojo, Monster, Mujer, Nieve, Nose, Nose Candy, P-Dogs, Peruvian, Powder, Press, Prime Time, Rush, Shot, Sleighride, Sniff, Snort, Snow, Snowbirds, Soda, Speedball, Sporting, Stardust, Sugar, Sweet Stuff, Toke, Trails, White Lady, White Powder, Yeyo, Zip. 可抽的古柯碱别名有：Base, Ball, Beat, Bisquits, Bones, Boost, Boulders, Brick, Bump, Cakes, Casper, Chalk, Cookies, Crumbs, Cubes, Fatbags, Freebase, Gravel, Hardball, Hell, Kibbles'n Bits, Kryptonite, Love, Moonrocks, Nuggets, Onion, Pebbles, Piedras, Piece, Ready Rock, Roca, Rock(s), Rock Star, Scotty, Scrabble, Smoke House, Stones, Teeth, Tornado.

　　第一一三页，快克拓荒者；布兰东与美国中情局的合作传闻，曾在报上以三天连载详尽报导，引发极大争议：San Jose Mercury News series by Gary Webb, beginning on August 18, 1996. 亦参见Tim Golden, "Though Evidence Is Thin, Tale of C.I.A. and Drugs Has a Life of Its Own," New York Times, October 21, 1996; and Gary Webb, Dark Alliance: The CIA, the Contras, and the Crack Cocaine Explosion (New York: Seven Stories Press, 1998). 美国司法部稍后对此曾进行详细调查，参见 "The C.I.A.—Contra—Crack Cocaine Controversy: A Review of the Justice Department's Investigations and Prosecutions," 亦可上网www.usdoj.gov/oig/special/9712/ch01pl.htm.

　　第一一三页，美国的帮派：参见Frederick Thrasher, The Gang (Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 1927).

　　第一一四页，快克之前黑白差距的缩小：参见Rebecca Blank, "An Overview of Social and Economic Trends By Race," in America Becoming: Racial Trends and Their Consequences, ed. Neil J. Smelser, William Julius Wilson, and Faith Mitchell (Washington, D.C.: National Academy Press, 2001), pp. 21-40.／第一一四页，黑人婴儿死亡率：参见Douglas V. Almond, Kenneth Y. Chay, and Michael Greenstone, "Civil Rights, the War on Poverty, and Black-White Convergence in Infant Mortality in Mississippi," National Bureau of Economic Research working paper, 2003.

　　第一一四—一一六页，有关快克各种负面影响，参见Roland G. Fryer Jr., Paul Heaton, Steven D. Levitt, and Kevin Murphy, "The Impact of Crack Cocaine," University of Chicago working paper, 2005.

４罪犯都跑到哪里去了？

　　第一一九—一二○页，西奥塞古的堕胎禁令：有关西奥塞古与罗马尼亚的背景资料取材自各种来源，包括 "Eastern Europe, the Third Communism," Time, March 18, 1966; "Ceau©jescu Ruled with an Iron Grip," Washington Post, December 26, 1989; Ralph Blumenthal, "The Ceau©jescus: 24 Years of Fierce Repression, Isolation and Independence," New York Times, December 26, 1989; Serge Schmemann, "In Cradle of Rumanian Revolt, Anger Quickly Overcame Fear," New York Times, December 30, 1989; Karen Breslau, "Overplanned Parenthood: Ceau©jescu's Cruel Law," Newsweek, January 22, 1990; and Nicolas Holman, "The Economic Legacy of Ceau©jescu" Student Economic Review, 1994.／第一一九页，罗马尼亚堕胎禁令及其影响，参见：Cristian Pop-Eleches, "The Impact of an Abortion Ban on Socio-Economic Outcomes of Children: Evidence from Romania," Columbia University working paper, 2002; and Cristian Pop-Eleches, "The Supply of Birth Control Methods, Education and Fertility: Evidence from Romania," Columbia University working paper, 2002.

　　第一二一—一二二页，美国犯罪大幅下降：如前所述，这一资料取材自Steven D. Levitt, "Understanding Why Crime Fell in the 1990's: Four Factors That Explain the Decline and Six That Do Not," Journal of Economic Perspectives 18, no. 1 (2004), pp. 163-90.／第一二一页，福克斯刻意的夸大：参见Torsten Ove, "No Simple Solution for Solving Violent Crimes," Pittsburgh Post-Gazette, September 12, 1999.

　　第一二三页，政治人物对犯罪的态度愈趋宽容：这一课题的相关探讨参见Gary S. Becker and Guity Nashat Becker, "Stiffer Jail Terms Will Make Gunmen More Gun-Shy," "How to Tackle Crime? Take a Tough, Head-On Stance," and "The Economic Approach to Fighting Crime," all in The Economics of Life (New York: McGraw-Hill, 1997), pp. 135-44；这些文章均摘自相同作者发表于Business Week的文章。

　　第一二三—一二五页，监狱囚禁人数增加：毒品罪入监服刑者增加十五倍，参见Ilyana Kuziemko and Steven D. Levitt, "An Empirical Analysis of Imprisoning Drug Offenders," Journal of Public Economics 88, nos. 9-10 (2004), pp. 2043-66.／第一二四页，如果把所有囚犯释放会如何？参见William Nagel, "On Behalf of a Moratorium on Prison Construction," Crime and Delinquency 23 (1977), pp. 152-74.／第一二五页，迪埃犹利欧的揶揄之词：参见John J. DiIulio Jr., "Arresting Ideas: Tougher Law Enforcement Is Driving Down Urban Crime," Policy Review, no. 75 (Fall 1995).

　　第一二五—一二六页，死刑：纽约州一九九五尚未处决一名犯人的详细说明，参见 "Capital Punishment in New York State: Statistics from Eight Years of Representation, 1995-2003" (New York: The Capital Defender Office, August 2003)，可查阅nycdo.org/8yr.html. 近期纽约上诉法院裁决死刑为违宪，使得所有死刑的执行几乎停摆。／第一二六页，处决一名犯人等于减少七件他可能犯下的杀人案：参见Isaac Ehrlich, "The Deterrent Effect of Capital Punishment: A Question of Life and Death," American Economic Review 65 (1975), pp. 397-417; and Isaac Ehrlich, "Capital Punishment and Deterrence: Some Further Thoughts and Evidence," Journal of Political Economy (1977), pp. 741-88.／第一二六页，「我不会再去对死刑机器修修补补。」摘自布莱克门法官在一九九四年最高法院驳回重审一件德州死刑案的反对意见：Callins v. Collins, 510 U.S. 1141 (1994); cited in Congressional Quarterly Researcher 5, no. 9 (March 10, 1995). 美国法院似乎也对死刑失去胃口——部分原因是由于近年无辜者遭处决或被判死刑者获赦免的情形时有所闻。一九九○年代，平均每年有二百九十人被判死刑，但自二○○○年起的四年，这个数字已降为一百七十四人。参见Adam Liptak, "Fewer Death Sentences Being Imposed in U.S.," New York Times, September 15, 2004.

　　第一二七—一二八页，警察真的可以降低犯罪吗？参见Steven D. Levitt, "Using Electoral Cycles in Police Hiring to Estimate the Effect of Police on Crime," American Economic Review 87, no. 3 (1997), pp. 270-90; Steven D. Levitt, "Why Do Increased Arrest Rates Appear to Reduce Crime: Deterrence, Incapacitation, or Measurement Error?" Economic Inquiry 36, no. 3 (1998), pp. 353-72; and Steven D. Levitt, "The Response of Crime Reporting Behavior to Changes in the Size of the Police Force: Implications for Studies of Police Effectiveness Using Reported Crime Data," Journal of Quantitative Criminology 14 (February 1998), pp. 62-81.／第一二八页，一九六○年代是犯罪的好时间：参见Gary S. Becker and Guity Nashat Becker, The Economics of Life (New York: McGraw-Hill, 1997), pp. 142-43.

　　第一二八—一三一页，纽约的治安奇迹：「我们的雅典时期」的说法来自作者与前警官William J. Gorta的访谈，他也是CompStat发明人之一。／第一二九页，破窗理论：参见James Q. Wilson and George L. Kelling, "Broken Windows: The Police and Neighborhood Safety," Atlantic Monthly, March 1982.／第一三一页，布拉顿在洛杉矶上任后增加警力：参见Terry McCarthy, "The Gang Buster," Time, January 19, 2004.

　　第一三二—一三四页枪械法规：美国枪枝数多于成人数，参见Philip Cook and Jens Ludwig, Guns in America: Results of a Comprehensive Survey of Gun Ownership and Use (Washington: Police Foundation, 1996).／第一三二页，枪枝与犯罪的关联：参见Mark Duggan, "More Guns, More Crime," Journal of Political Economy 109, no. 5 (2001), pp. 1086-1114.／第一三二页，瑞士的枪枝：参见Stephen P. Halbrook, "Armed to the Teeth, and Free," Wall Street Journal Europe. June 4, 1999.／第一三三页布莱迪法案毫无作用：参见Jens Ludwig and Philip Cook, "Homicide and Suicide Rates Associated with Implementation of the Brady Handgun Violence Prevention Act," Journal of the American Medical Association 284, no. 5. (2000), pp. 585-91.／第一三三页，歹徒购买黑枪：参见James D. Wright and Peter H. Rossi, Armed and Considered Dangerous: A Survey of Felons and Their Firearms (Hawthorne, N.Y.: Aldine de Gruyter, 1986).／第一三四页，以免费心理治疗作为缴回枪枝报酬：参见 "Wise Climb-Down, Bad Veto," Los Angeles Times, October 5, 1994.／第一三三页，为何枪枝买回没有效果：参见C. Callahan, F. Rivera, and T. Koepsell, "Money for Guns: Evaluation of the Seattle Gun Buy-Back Program," Public Health Reports 109, no. 4 (1994), pp. 472-77; David Kennedy, Anne Piehl, and Anthony Braga, "Youth Violence in Boston: Gun Markets, Serious Youth Offenders, and a Use-Reduction Strategy," Law and Contemporary Problems 59 (1996), pp. 147-83; and Peter Reuter and Jenny Mouzon, "Australia: A Massive Buy-back of Low-Risk Guns," in Evaluating Gun Policy: Effects on Crime and Violence, ed. Jens Ludwig and Philip Cook (Washington, D.C.: Brookings Institution, 2003).／第一三四页，洛特的携枪理论：参见John R. Lott Jr. and David Mustard, "Right-to-Carry Concealed Guns and the Importance of Deterrence," Journal of Legal Studies 26 (January 1997), pp. 1-68; and John R. Lott Jr., More Guns, Less Crime: Understanding Crime and Gun Control Laws (Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 1998).／第一三四页，洛特利用玛丽·罗许的化名：参见Julian Sanchez, "The Mystery of Mary Rosh," Reason, May 2003; and Richard Morin, "Scholar Invents Fan to Answer His Critics," Washington Post, February 1, 2003.／第一三四页，对洛特理论的反驳：参见Ian Ayres and John J. Donohue III, "Shooting Down the 'More Guns, Less Crime Hypothesis," Stanford Law Review 55 (2003), pp. 1193-1312; and Mark Duggan, "More Guns, More Crime," Journal of Political Economy 109, no. 5 (2001), pp. 1086-1114.

　　第一三五—一三六页，快克泡沫的破灭；有关快克历史与相关细节，参见Roland G. Fryer Jr., Paul Heaton, Steven Levitt, and Kevin Murphy, "The Impact of Crack Cocaine," University of Chicago working paper, 2005.／第一三五页，二五％杀人案件：参见Paul J. Goldstein, Henry H. Brownstein, Patrick J. Ryan, and Patricia A. Bellucci, "Crack and Homicide in New York City: A Case Study in the Epidemiology of Violence," in Crack in America: Demon Drugs and Social Justice, ed. Craig Reinarman and Harry G. Levine (Berkeley: University of California Press, 1997), pp. 113-30.

　　第一三六页，人口老化理论：参见Steven D. Levitt, "The Limited Role of Changing Age Structure in Explaining Aggregate Crime Rates," Criminology 37, no. 3 (1999), pp. 581-99. 虽然老化理论目前已经广受质疑，但不少专家仍继续鼓吹；参见Matthew L. Wald, "Most Crimes of Violence and Property Hover at 30-Year Low," New York Times, September 13, 2004，该文中司法统计局长Lawrence A. Greenfield指出：「有关这些年来犯罪率为何一直下跌，而且目前处于我们一九七三年开始测量以来的最低水准，或许并没有单一因素可以解释。可能与人口因素有关，也可能是因为许多恶性重大者给关在牢里。」／第一三六页，「地平线的一端乌云密布」：参见James Q. Wilson, "Crime and Public Policy" in Crime, ed. James Q. Wilson and Joan Petersilia (San Francisco: ICS Press, 1995), p. 507.

　　第一三七—一四五页，堕胎与犯罪的关联：参见John J. Donohue III and Steven D. Levitt, "The Impact of Legalized Abortion on Crime," Quarterly Journal of Economics 116, no. 2 (2001), pp. 379-420; and John J. Donohue III and Steven D. Levitt, "Further Evidence That Legalized Abortion Lowered Crime: A Response to Joyce," Journal of Human Resources 39, no. 1 (2004), pp. 29-49.／第一三七页，东欧其他地区与北欧的堕胎研究：参见P. K. Dagg, "The Psychological Sequelae of Therapeutic Abortion—Denied and Completed," American Journal of Psychiatry 148, no. 5 (May 1991), pp. 578-85; and Henry David, Zdenek Dytrych, et al., Born Unwanted: Developmental Effects of Denied Abortion (New York: Springer, 1988).／第一三八页，洛伊对韦德案的多数意见：Roe v. Wade, 410 U.S. 113 (1973).／第一三八页，典型被堕胎掉的小孩：参见Jonathan Gruber, Philip P. Levine, and Douglas Staiger, "Abortion Legalization and Child Living Circumstances: Who Is the 'Marginal Child?'" Quarterly Journal of Economics 114 (1999), pp. 263-91.／第一三九页，预测未来成为罪犯的最重要因素：参见Rolf Loeber and Magda Stouthamer-Loeber, "Family Factors as Correlates and Predictors of Juvenile Conduct Problems and Delinquency," Crime and Justice, vol. 7, ed. Michael Tonry and Norval Morris (Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 1986); also, Robert Sampson and John Laub, Crime in the Making: Pathways and Turning Points Through Life (Cambridge, Mass.: Harvard University Press, 1993).／第一三九页，母亲二十岁以下亦是如此：参见William S. Comanor and Llad Phillips, "The Impact of Income and Family Structure on Delinquency," University of California—Santa Barbara working paper, 1999.／第一三九页，母亲的教育水准是子女未来是否犯罪最重要的单一因素：Pirkko Ra©asa©aneu et al., "Maternal Smoking During Pregnancy and Risk of Criminal Behavior Among Adult Male Offspring in the Northern Finland 1966 Birth Cohort," American Journal of Psychiatry 156 (1999), pp. 857-62.／第一三九页，杀婴事件大幅下降：参见Susan Sorenson, Douglas Wiebe, and Richard Berk, "Legalized Abortion and the Homicide of Young Children: An Empirical Investigation," Analyses of Social 1ssues and Public Policy 2, no. 1 (2002), pp. 239-56.／第一四一页，澳洲与加拿大的研究：参见Anindya Sen, "Does Increased Abortion Lead to Lower Crime? Evaluating the Relationship between Crime, Abortion, and Fertility," unpublished manuscript; and Andrew Leigh and Justin Wolfers, "Abortion and Crime," AQ: Journal of Contemporary Analysis 72, no. 4 (2000), pp. 28-30.／第一四一页，因堕胎而未生下的女孩：参见John J. Donohue III, Jeffrey Grogger, and Steven D. Levitt, "The Impact of Legalized Abortion on Teen Childbearing," University of Chicago working paper, 2002.／第一四二页，堕胎罪孽更甚于奴隶制度：参见Michael S. Paulsen, "Accusing Justice: Some Variations on the Themes of Robert M. Cover's Justice Accused," Journal of Law and Religion 7, no. 33 (1989), pp. 33-97.／第一四二页，堕胎「堪称唯一有效的犯罪防范措施」：参见Anthony V. Bouza, The Police Mystique: An Insider's Look at Cops, Crime, and the Criminal Justice System (New York: Plenum, 1990).／第一四二页，拯救一只斑点枭要花九百万美元：参见Gardner M. Brown and Jason F. Shogren, "Economics of the Endangered Species Act," Journal of Economic Perspectives 12, no. 3 (1998), pp. 3-20.／第一四二页，愿意花三十一美元来预防类似埃克森·瓦尔德兹号漏油事件：参见Glenn W. Harrison, "Assessing Damages for the Exxon Valdez Oil Spill," University of Central Florida working paper, 2004.／第一四三—一四四页，人体器官价格表：摘自the state of Connecticut's Workers' Compensation Information Packet, p. 27，可查阅wcc.state.ct.us/download/acrobat/info-packet.pdf.

５怎样才算理想的父母？

　　第一四七—一四八页，亲子专家的观点时刻都在改变：赫尔柏特的著作（New York: Knopf, 2003）罗列各种与子女教养有关的建议。／第一四八页，艾索的「婴儿管理策略」与对睡眠方式不当的警告：参见Gary Ezzo and Robert Bucknam, On Becoming Babywise (Sisters, Ore.: Multnomah, 1995), pp. 32 and 53.／第一四八页，布拉索顿与「互动」的小孩：T. Berry Brazelton, Infants and Mothers: Difference in Development, rev. ed. (New York: Delta/Seymour Lawrence, 1983), p. xxiii.／第一四八页，侯尔特对「不当刺激」的警告：L. Emmett Holt, The Happy Baby (New York: Dodd, Mead, 1924), p. 7.／第一四八页，啼哭「是宝宝的运动」：L. Emmett Holt, The Care and Feeding of Children: A Catechism for the Use of Mothers and Children's Nurses (New York: Appleton, 1894), p. 53.

　　第一四九—一五三页，手枪与游泳池：参见Steven Levitt, "Pools More Dangerous than Guns," Chicago Sun-Times, July 28, 2001.

　　第一五○—一五一页，山德曼对美国狂牛症与其他风险的评论：参见Amanda Hesser, "Squeaky Clean? Not Even Close," New York Times, January 28, 2004; and "The Peter Sandman Risk Communication Web Site" at http://www.psandman.com/index.htm.

　　第一五三—一五六页，父母究竟有多重要？参见Judith Rich Harris, The Nurture Assumption: Why Children Turn Out the Way They Do (New York: Free Press, 1998)；哈瑞丝的介绍也可以做为天生教养争论的极佳参考。参见Malcolm Gladwell, "Do Parents Matter?" The New Yorker, August 17, 1998; and Carol Tavris, "Peer Pressure," New York Times Book Review, September 13, 1998.／第一五四页，「『又来了』」的评论：参见Tavris, New York Times.／第一五四页，品克认为哈瑞丝的观点「震撼人心」：Steven Pinker, "Sibling Rivalry: Why the Nature/Nurture Debate Won't Go Away," Boston Globe, October 13, 2002, adapted from Steven Pinker, The Blank Slate: The Modern Denial of Human Nature (New York:Viking, 2002).

　　第一五七—一五九页，芝加哥的选校：取材自Julie Berry Cullen, Brian Jacob, and Steven D. Levitt, "The Impact of School Choice on Student Outcomes: An Analysis of the Chicago Public Schools," Journal of Public Economics, forthcoming; and Julie Berry Cullen, Brian Jacob, and Steven D. Levitt, "The Effect of School Choice on Student Outcomes: Evidence from Randomized Lotteries," National Bureau of Economic Research working paper, 2003.

　　第一五九页，进入高中的学生没办法应付高中的课业：参见Tamar Lewin, "More Students Passing Regents, but Achievement Gap Persists," New York Times, March 18, 2004.

　　第一五九—一六○页，回溯八年级考试成绩差异来分析黑白的所得差距：参见Derek Neal and William R. Johnson, "The Role of Pre-Market Factors in Black-White Wage Differences," Journal of Political Economy 104 (1996), pp. 869-95; and June O'Neill, "The Role of Human Capital in Earnings Differences Between Black and White Men," Journal of Economic Perspectives 4, no. 4 (1990), pp. 25-46.／第一五九页，「减少黑白的考试成绩差距」：参见Christopher Jencks and Meredith Phillips, "America's Next Achievement Test: Closing the Black-White Test Score Gap," American Prospect 40 (September-October 1998), pp. 44-53.

　　第一五九页，「装白人」：参见David Austen-Smith and Roland G. Fryer Jr., "The Economics of 'Acting White,'" National Bureau of Economic Research working paper, 2003.／第一五九页，阿柏杜尔—贾巴：Kareem Abdul-Jabbar and Peter Knobler, Giant Steps (New York: Bantam, 1983), p. 16.

　　第一六○—一七四页，黑白学生ＥＣＬＳ测验成绩差距：摘自Roland G. Fryer Jr. and Steven D. Levitt, "Understanding the Black-White Test Score Gap in the First Two Years of School," The Review of Economics and Statistics 86, no. 2 (2004), pp. 447-464. 虽然这篇论文对测验分数与一些家庭因素（看电视、父母的体罚等）的相关未曾著墨，但附录中包含这些资料的回归。有关ＥＣＬＳ研究本身：本书写作时，一项对这一研究的检讨张贴于nces.ed.gov/ecls/。

　　第一七○页，领养父母的智商高于生身母亲：参见Bruce Sacerdote, "The Nature and Nurture of Economic Outcomes," National Bureau of Economic Research working paper, 2000.

　　第一七一页，芬兰儿童识字早：参见Lizette Alvarez, "Educators Flocking to Finland, Land of Literate Children," New York Times, April 9, 2004.

　　第一七二页，送书给每位幼儿：参见John Keilman, "Governor Wants Books for Tots; Kids Would Get 60 by Age 5 in Effort to Boost Literacy," Chicago Tribune, January 12, 2004.

　　第一七四—一七五页，养父母的影响：参见Sacerdote, "The Nature and Nurture of Economic Outcomes."

６完美的父母，续篇：换个名字会更好？

　　第一七七—一七八页，失败的故事：取材自作者的访谈与Sean Gardiner, "Winner and Loser: Names Don't Decide Destiny," Newsday, July 22, 2002.

　　第一七八页，法官与叫「魔女」女孩：取材自作者的访谈。

　　第一八○页，弗莱尔与黑人偏低成就的研究：摘自作者的访谈。

　　第一八○页，黑白抽烟的差异：参阅Lloyd Johnston, Patrick O'Malley, Jerald Bachman, and John Schulenberg, "Cigarette Brand Preferences Among Adolescents," Monitoring the Future Occasional Paper 45, Institute for Social Research, University of Michigan, 1999.

　　第一八○—一八七页，黑人名字 (与其他黑白文化差异)：参见Roland G. Fryer Jr. and Steven D. Levitt, "The Causes and Consequences of Distinctively Black Names," Quarterly Journal of Economics 119, no. 3 (August 2004), pp. 767-805.

　　第一八四页，「白人」履历表胜过「黑人」履历表：最近一次这类研究参见Marianne Bertrand and Sendhil Mullainathan, "Are Emily and Greg More Employable than Lakisha and Jamal? A Field Experiment Evidence on Labor Market Discrimination," National Bureau of Economic Research working paper, 2003.

　　第一八五页，YO XING HEYNO AUGUSTUS EISNER ALEXANDER WEISER KNUCKLES JEREMI-JENKO-CONLEY：参见Tara Bahrampour, "A Boy Named Yo, Etc.: Name Changes, Both Practical and Fanciful, Are on the Rise," New York Times, September 25, 2003.

　　第一八五页，MICHAEL GOLDBERG，印度出生的锡克教徒：参见Robert F. Worth, "Livery Driver Is Wounded in a Shooting," New York Times, February 9, 2004.

　　第一八六页，WILLIAM MORRIS, NE©Y ZELMAN MOSES：取材自作者与该机构前营运长Alan Kannof的访谈。

　　第一八七页，以品牌命名：摘自加州出生证明资料与Stephanie Kang, "Naming the Baby: Parents Brand Their Tot with What's Hot," Wall Street Journal, December 26, 2003.

　　第一八八页，名叫笨蛋（Shithead）的女孩：打电话到广播节目说外甥女叫笨蛋的女子可能资讯有误，当然也可能纯粹是说谎。无论如何，她认为黑人取名字有时太过头，倒是和不少人的感受相同。二○○四年五月，在禁止学校黑白隔离法案施行五十年的庆祝会上，黑人影星寇斯比发表演讲时，痛斥低所得黑人各种自我毁灭式的行为，包括取「贫民窟」的名字。他的说法立即遭到黑人与白人评论者的强烈指责。（参见Barbara Ehrenreich, "The New Cosby Kids," New York Times, July 8, 2004; and Debra Dickerson, "America's Granddad Gets Ornery," Slate, July 13, 2004.）不久之后，加州教育厅长里奥丹（Richard Riordan）——洛杉矶前市长，有钱的白人——也因被认为有种族偏见而受到攻击。（参见Tim Rutten, "Riordan Stung by 'Gotcha' News," Los Angeles Times, July 10, 2004.）里奥丹拜访圣塔芭芭拉一所图书馆倡导某项阅读方案时，遇到一个叫艾西斯（Isis）的六岁女孩。她告诉里奥丹她的名字是代表「埃及公主」；里奥丹却开玩笑地回答：「那是指愚笨、肮脏的女孩。」这句话引起公愤，黑人社运者还要求里奥丹引咎辞职。黑人议员戴马理（Mervyn Dymally）声称艾西斯是「非裔美国小女孩。如果换作一个白人女孩，他还会说同样的话吗？」后来证实艾西斯其实是白人。虽然有些社运人士希望让反里奥丹的抗议持续下去，但艾西斯的母亲却劝大家放轻松。她说她的女儿并没有把里奥丹的玩笑话当真：「我觉得她认为这个人脑筋不太好。」

　　第一九四页，更详尽的名字资料；以下是我们所选出的一组名字，或有趣、或优美、或不寻常、或极为普通、或有些怪异，并附上它们代表的教育程度。每个名字在加州资料中至少出现十次。

　　第一九七页，加州白人女孩一九六○年与二○○○年最普遍的名字：这项资料其实始自一九六一年，但一年的差异可以忽略不计。

　　第一九九页，秀兰·邓波儿是症状，而非病因：参见Stanley Lieberson, A Matter of Taste: How Names, Fashions, and Culture Change (New Haven, Conn.: Yale University Press, 2000). 该书作者李柏森是哈佛社会学者，被公认是名字研究的权威。书中详述自一九六○年起，美国犹太裔家庭率先让许多女孩名字流行起来（Amy, Danielle, Erica, Jennifer, Jessica, Melissa, Rachel, Rebecca, Sarah, Stacy, Stephanie, Tracy），从非犹太裔家庭开始流行的名字寥寥可数（Ashley, KeIIy, Kimberly）。有关命名习惯的讨论亦参见Peggy Orenstein, "Where Have All the Lisas Gone?" New York Times Magazine, July 6, 2003；如果纯粹以娱乐观点，可参见The Sweetest Sound (2001)，这是Alan Berliner有关名字的纪录片。

　　第一九九页，男孩名字转变为女孩名字（但相反的情况却不曾发生）：这项发现摘自贝勒维大学心理学者与专有名词学者伊凡斯（Cleveland Kent Evans）的著作。伊凡斯的部分著作可上网academic.bellevue.edu/CKEvans/cevans.html；亦参见Cleveland Kent Evans, Unusual & Most Popular Baby Names (Lincolnwood, Ill.: Publications International/Signet, 1994); and Cleveland Kent Evans, The Ultimate Baby Name Book (Lincolnwood, I11.: Publications International/Plume, 1997).

尾声：到哈佛的两条路

　　第二○四页，在芝加哥郊区长大的白人男孩：这一段文字以及第五章提及这名男孩的文字均摘自作者对卡辛斯基的专访以及Ted Kaczynski, Truth Versus Lies, unpublished manuscript, 1998；亦参见Stephen J. Dubner, "I Don't Want to Live Long. I Would Rather Get the Death Penalty than Spend the Rest of My Life in Prison," Time, October 18, 1999.

　　第二○四页，来自佛罗里达的黑人男孩：本章及前章的相关叙述均取材自作对弗莱尔的访谈。

＊由纯洁（Chastity）在此的表现来看，那个叫「魔女」（Temptress）的十五岁女孩如果叫纯洁，表现也不见得会好多少。 ⏎
